<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.10.5">
<l>māṉamaru melnōkki vaitēvī viṇṇappam</l>
<l>kāṉamaruṅ kallatarpōyk kāṭuṟainta kālattu</l>
<l>tēṉamarum poḻiṟcāral cittirakū ṭattiruppa</l>
<l>pālmoḻiyāy paratanampi paṇintatumō raṭaiyāḷam.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Lady of soft deer-like gaze! Vaidehī! Salutations!</l>
<l>When, having taken the stoney path to the forest,</l>
<l rend="indent">you dwelt in the forest, You of milk[-sweet] words,</l>
<l>on the Citrakūṭa hill-side with honey-filled groves,</l>
<l>and Prince Bharata [came and] bowed.</l>
<l>This is one proof.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
